    "_lineHeight": 28,
    "_string": "The theoretical RTP of this game is <color=#FDE900>95.53%</color><color=#FFFFFF>\nThe RTP of the game when using \"BUY FREE SPINS\" is</color> <color=#FDE900>95.53%</color>\nSPACE buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.\nMalfunction voids all pays and plays.",
